    <section class="content-blurb top">
        <h1>What is Cobblemon?</h1>
        <p>Cobblemon is an open-source Pokémon mod that is available through Fabric and Forge for Minecraft version 1.19.2.</p>
        <p>Capture Pokémon to expand your team, battle wild Pokémon to gain experience, and level up to unlock new moves!</p>
        <a class="button" href="https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon" target="_blank">Download</a>
    </section>
