    </section>
    <section class="content">
        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-text">
                    <h3 id="build_your_team">Build Your Team</h3>
                    <p>Gather Pokémon to join you on your adventure.</p>
                    <p>Your Pokémon will follow you when sent out of their Poké Ball, and some small Pokémon can even ride on your shoulder!</p>
                    <p>The wide array of immersive features, including Pokémon faint and sleeping animations, will help bring your world to life.</p>
